parameters: \n<Hooded woman>"Hey, what are you doing? Hurry up and escape!"
\n<Sister girl>"I... I can't anymore, I can't move..."

\n<Sister girl>"At this rate, we'll both get caught! I'll stay behind as a
decoy, so escape while you can!"

\n<Hooded woman>"...Hmph. A decoy? Like that's going to work. You won't buy
us any time, you'll just get caught in the end."
\n<Voice of the thief>"They ran this way! Hurry up!"
\n<Hooded woman>"Tch... Ah, damn it. Why did it come to this..."

\n<Hooded woman>"I'll show you how to be a decoy. I'll buy you some time, so
hide somewhere."

\n<Sister girl>"No! That's absolutely not okay! Fighting alone is too
dangerous!"

\n<Hooded woman>"Well, don't worry about it. Those guys will be nothing but
ashes. Ashes to ashes."

\n<Sister girl>"That's why I'm saying it's no good, you idiot! Listen to
me!"
\n<Hooded woman>"...You're so noisy. Just be quiet and--"

The sister girl clung to the arm of the woman who had
started to walk away.
\n<Sister girl>"...It's okay. It's going to be okay."

\n<Sister girl>"I can't bear the thought of someone getting hurt for me. So
please, escape."

\n<Hooded woman>"Really, you're so selfish. Telling me not to escape, then
telling me to run away."
\n<Sister girl>"...I'm sorry. But I made a promise."
\n<Sister girl>"I will protect you. So please, run away."
